### cdk-pixbuf 2.45.1

  * meson_options: disable builtin_loaders and enable jpeg and png


### cdk-pixbuf 2.45.0

  * initial release forked from gdk-pixbuf 2.44.5
  * ci: enable Github Actions
  * update CONTRIBUTING.md and README.md
  * ctk website instead gtk in some places
  * rename gtk -> ctk
  * rename gdk -> cdk
  * gen-resources: rename CDK_PIXBUF_PIXDATA -> GDK_PIXBUF_PIXDATA
  * add svg loader taken from librsvg
  * io-svg: rename gdk -> cdk
  * io-svg.c: Fix assignment to CdkPixbuf from incompatible pointer type GdkPixbuf
  * meson_options:
    - disable glycin
    - enable thumbnailer, others, tiff, gif, svg
    - set builtin_loaders png and jpeg
  * update translations
